act is, the "late" part isn't because of IORESOURCE_BUSY. It's <br />because FIRMWARE IS INEVITABLY A STINKING PILE OF BUGGY SH*T THAT MUST <br />NOT BE ALLOWED TO SCREW UP DEVICE DISCOVERY.<br /><br />Sorry for shouting, but people really need to understand this.<br /><br />			Linus<br /><br /><br /></pre><div align="center"><div class="shariff" data-services="[&quot;reddit&quot;]" data-theme="grey" data-lang="en" data-backend-url="//shariff.lkml.org/index.php"></div></div></td><td width="32" rowspan="2" class="c" valign="top"><img src="/images/icornerr.gif" width="32" height="32" alt="\" /></td></tr><tr><td align="right" valign="bottom">
